00054 void FusionCHPMultiDataDataTest::testRead()
00055 {
00056         FusionCHPData *chp = FusionCHPDataReg::Read("../../parsers/data/CHP_MultiData_file");
00057         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(chp != NULL);
00058         FusionCHPMultiDataData *genoChp = FusionCHPMultiDataData::FromBase(chp); 
00059         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(genoChp != NULL);
00060 
00061 
00062     affymetrix_calvin_data::ProbeSetMultiDataExpressionData ex;
00063     affymetrix_calvin_data::ProbeSetMultiDataGenotypeData gn;
00064         ParameterNameValueType param;
00065 
00066         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(genoChp->GetAlgName() == L"sig");
00067         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(genoChp->GetAlgVersion() == L"1.0");
00068         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(genoChp->GetArrayType() == L"test3");
00069         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(genoChp->GetEntryCount(ExpressionMultiDataType) == 1);
00070         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(genoChp->GetEntryCount(GenotypeMultiDataType) == 2);
00071         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(genoChp->GetEntryCount(ExpressionControlMultiDataType) == 3);
00072         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(genoChp->GetEntryCount(GenotypeControlMultiDataType) == 1);
00073 
00074     // expression
00075     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(genoChp->GetNumMetricColumns(ExpressionMultiDataType) == 0);
00076     genoChp->GetExpressionEntry(ExpressionMultiDataType, 0, ex);
00077         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(ex.quantification, 10.0f, 0.0001f);
00078         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(ex.name == "ex1");
00079 
00080     // genotype
00081     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(genoChp->GetNumMetricColumns(GenotypeMultiDataType) == 2);
00082     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(genoChp->GetMetricColumnName(GenotypeMultiDataType, 0) == L"int");
00083     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(genoChp->GetMetricColumnName(GenotypeMultiDataType, 1) == L"float");
00084 
00085     genoChp->GetGenotypeEntry(GenotypeMultiDataType, 0, gn);
00086         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.call == 1);
00087         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(gn.confidence, 11.0f, 0.0001f);
00088         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.name == "gn1");
00089     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.metrics.size() == 2);
00090     param = gn.metrics[0];
00091     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetParameterType() == ParameterNameValueType::Int32Type);
00092     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueInt32() == 1);
00093     param = gn.metrics[1];
00094     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetParameterType() == ParameterNameValueType::FloatType);
00095     CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(param.GetValueFloat(), 2.0f, 0.00001f);
00096 
00097     genoChp->GetGenotypeEntry(GenotypeMultiDataType, 1, gn);
00098         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.call == 2);
00099         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(gn.confidence, 22.0f, 0.0001f);
00100         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.name == "gn2");
00101     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.metrics.size() == 2);
00102     param = gn.metrics[0];
00103     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetParameterType() == ParameterNameValueType::Int32Type);
00104     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueInt32() == 2);
00105     param = gn.metrics[1];
00106     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetParameterType() == ParameterNameValueType::FloatType);
00107     CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(param.GetValueFloat(), 3.0f, 0.00001f);
00108 
00109 
00110     // genotype control
00111     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(genoChp->GetNumMetricColumns(GenotypeControlMultiDataType) == 0);
00112     genoChp->GetGenotypeEntry(GenotypeControlMultiDataType, 0, gn);
00113         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.call == 2);
00114         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(gn.confidence, 22.0f, 0.0001f);
00115         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.metrics.size() == 0);
00116         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.name == "gc1");
00117 
00118 
00119 
00120     // expression control
00121     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(genoChp->GetNumMetricColumns(ExpressionControlMultiDataType) == 0);
00122         genoChp->GetExpressionEntry(ExpressionControlMultiDataType, 0, ex);
00123         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(ex.quantification, 20.0f, 0.0001f);
00124         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(ex.name == "ec1");
00125         genoChp->GetExpressionEntry(ExpressionControlMultiDataType, 1, ex);
00126         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(ex.quantification, 30.0f, 0.0001f);
00127         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(ex.name == "ec2");
00128         genoChp->GetExpressionEntry(ExpressionControlMultiDataType, 2, ex);
00129         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(ex.quantification, 40.0f, 0.0001f);
00130         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(ex.name == "ec3");
00131 
00132         delete genoChp;

00149         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(cnChp->GetEntryCount(GenotypeMultiDataType) == 0);
00150         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(cnChp->GetEntryCount(ExpressionMultiDataType) == 0);
00151         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(cnChp->GetEntryCount(ExpressionControlMultiDataType) == 0);
00152         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(cnChp->GetEntryCount(GenotypeControlMultiDataType) == 0);
00153 
00154         ParameterNameValueTypeList p = cnChp->GetAlgParams();
00155         ParameterNameValueTypeList::iterator it = p.begin();
00156         param = *it;
00157         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetName() == L"an1");
00158         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueText() == L"av1");
00159 
00160         p = cnChp->GetSummaryParams();
00161         it = p.begin();
00162         param = *it;
00163         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetName() == L"sn1");
00164         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueText() == L"sv1");
00165 
00166     cnChp->GetCopyNumberEntry(CopyNumberMultiDataType, 0, e);
00167         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.chr == 10);
00168         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.position == 11);
00169         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.name == "abc");
00170         cnChp->GetCopyNumberEntry(CopyNumberMultiDataType, 1, e);
00171         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.chr == 20);
00172         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.position == 21);
00173         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.name == "xyz");
00174 
00175         delete cnChp;
00176 }
